('9468a7f2-4a91-53f4-9b0d-5030038c7aab', 'd99f5952-91d8-41d5-8a1c-267609e39a20', 'SENIOR_HIGH', 'There were ___ 100 people in the audience.', '觀眾大約有100人。', 'about', 'surely', 'quickly', 'deeply', '表示數量或時間的近似值 (大約)', 'about + [數字] → 大約的數量', '2026-07-05 07:40:09', '2026-07-05 07:40:09'),
('dbe4783e-d22d-532a-b1a5-5fa7a1b8b9d3', 'c65a0c33-e9b1-448a-98db-bb934683f81c', 'JUNIOR_HIGH', 'It is sunny, ___ it is very cold.', '天氣晴朗，但是非常冷。', 'but', 'and', 'so', 'or', '表示轉折 (但是)', '看到 but 就要想到轉折 (轉折 → but)', '2026-07-05 13:01:30', '2026-07-05 13:01:30'),
('bf103383-55f6-542c-a768-9eff9adbf653', '5e767169-2c20-400a-b068-5b0d10f7fd45', 'JUNIOR_HIGH', 'I will ___ my homework tonight.', '我今晚會做功課。', 'do', 'make', 'take', 'play', 'do (做/進行)', 'do homework → 做功課', '2026-07-05 08:35:16', '2026-07-05 08:35:16'),
('07bae832-4120-5220-896e-098520344cc7', 'ad050278-a913-4be5-b0bb-d3d91b5aa55b', 'SENIOR_HIGH', 'The students were told to ___ back to their classrooms after the break.', '學生們被告知在休息時間結束後要回到教室。', 'go', 'stay', 'live', 'work', 'go (v.) 表示移動或前往某處。', '想像自己正朝著目的地「走」去。', '2026-07-05 08:01:37', '2026-07-05 08:01:37'),
('8c75067c-3f44-5fbd-8035-d439752b04a3', 'aa399e16-a6c4-493c-b107-b99c7a6b4391', 'JUNIOR_HIGH', 'I want a cup ___ water.', '我想要一杯水。', 'of', 'at', 'in', 'on', 'of 用於表示量詞與內容物。', '一杯 + of + 水 = 一杯水', '2026-07-05 09:05:48', '2026-07-05 09:05:48'),
('1b5c80d1-8e04-53a5-9c56-0adfe6f60247', '5addd1d3-67f0-46a1-b83e-c6d01c9eb38d', 'SENIOR_HIGH', 'The math problem was ___ difficult that nobody could solve it.', '這道數學題是如此困難，以至於沒人能解開它。', 'so', 'hardly', 'seldom', 'nearly', 'so 為副詞，用於 so...that 句型，表示程度之大導致某種結果。', 'so...that 是一個組合拳，so 負責程度，that 負責結果。', '2026-07-06 10:57:16', '2026-07-06 10:57:16');
